items.headline: For 2027, Gorgeous Edgemoor Lot with Rear Southern Exposure—Custom Design & Build
items.blurb: Custom design-build opportunity in an incredible walkable location.
items.description: Design your home from scratch with award-winning architects or start from one of our concept plans and tailor it to your lifestyle. Close to downtown Bethesda shops, dining, Metro, and quick access to Washington, D.C.
